STUDY.STUDY_SUMMARY: To determine the basis of running capacity and health differences in outbread N/NIH rats selected for high capacity (HCR) and low capacity (LCR) running (a for VO2max) (see:Science. 2005 Jan 21;307(5708):418-20). Plasma collected at 12 of age in generation 28 rats after ad lib feeding or 40% caloric restriction at week 8 of age. All animals fasted 4 hours prior to collection between 5-8

SUBJECT.GENOTYPE_STRAIN: Low Capacity Running | High Capacity Running
